{
  "stem": "24885.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you find your own job where to go to, which was much better than just every day being recruited to something different and you ended up you didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were fortunate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of us, at first we volunteered to be gardeners and so on, and we grew vegetables, we grew flowers for the German, for the Wehrmacht, for the army.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And was much easier than work for the SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then I think I mentioned I saw a-- a soldier came down, a Wehrmacht soldier came down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a big place, large place with a lot of grass.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He came down to feed the horse, you know, for a few hours.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I went up to him and asked him if he needed help.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that I know my way around horses, and he gladly accepted me, and I get the job.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I used to go every morning early to the stable to clean the horse with him and do everything else that's necessary.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then about 8 o'clock, whatever, the officers would come to ride and the horse was ready.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In the meantime I cleaned up the stalls and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But at the same time, I got enough food for myself, and to take home, too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From him, from the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Wehrmacht, some of them were bad, but some of them were terrible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you avoided the bad ones and like they had a mess hall where they ate, and if there was leftover, there were some other people, a friend of mine who worked cleaning the barracks, or cleaning the houses, or so on, then we would be in line last to eat the leftovers.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at least we had something to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had food.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
